description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Rhythm 30 HIIT Row' from the channel Aisyah Rafaee.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Adrenaline Rush vibe.
The The Firestarter vibe means Fast, explosive, and electrifying. Short but devastating. This is especially good for When you only have 10-20 minutes but want to give 1000%. The The Adrenaline Rush vibe means Heart-racing, full-body intensity, unpredictable challenges. This is especially good for Those who crave challenge, variety, and adrenaline..
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Exert max pressure on the footboards during 1-minute intervals at rhythm 30 with Aisyah followed by 1-minute recovery. 

Max rhythm: 30, Format: HIIT ...
